channel.title: Live: Wimbledon 2025
channel.desc: Live tennis from the All England Club, Wimbledon, with the last four players remaining in the men's singles battling it out for a place in Sunday's showpiece final. In 2024's opening semi-final, Spain's Carlos Alcaraz dropped the opening set in a tie-break against Daniil Medvedev, but he recovered to reach back-to-back Wimbledon finals.
